-I make the cart controller ,routes and models 
-optionalAuth middleware that checks if user is logged in or a guest to handle that the guest can add item to cart
-getOrCreateCart request that handles both guest and logged-in users creates 
-used cookies for guest cart that live for 30 days 
-I handled the guest to user cart merge when the guest logs in the cart data will be merged to the user cart and the guest cart will be deleted 
-addtoCart request that validates product exists checks stock including what is already in cart  creates or updates cart item
-removeItemFromCart request that finds item in cart and deletes it
-updateCartItemQuantity request that update the quantity of an item in the cart and it checks stock before updating 
-getCart request that populates product details calculates itemTotal and totalPrice
-clearCart request that deletes all items from the cart
